title: Patangbaaz From Bareilly - Sundeep Sharma Stand-up Comedy
description:
This video starts with some incidents from my life in my hometown Bareilly, a beautiful city in western Uttar Pradesh which is famous for kites and a few more things. It covers a small part of my growing up years and the influences I had. There are some jokes and some spontaneous and uncensored interaction with a few members of the audience. I have kept the interaction part in the video because I know you all are at home and are already bored, the interaction part might be better than too much boredom, and its all spontaneous so may be you'll like it, if you do, then share this video with friends and also subscribe to my channel if you still have not.

title: Fact check : क्या Tirupati Balaji ने 200 करोड़ और Ambani ने 1000 करोड़ Coronavirus के लिए दिए हैं?
description:
Read the complete story here: https://www.thelallantop.com/factcheck/fact-check-whatsapp-message-claims-hindu-celebrities-and-temples-donated-amounts-in-crores-for-the-fight-against-coronavirus-pandemic/

The Lallantop Fact check: Amid coronavirus outbreak in India, a message is being shared indiscriminately on social media claiming that Hindu temples and Hindu actors like Akshay Kumar, Varun Dhawan and industrialists like Mukesh Ambani have given a lot of donations in the time of coronavirus disaster. It is also being said in this message that nothing has been given from the places of worship and celebrations of other religions. 

In the investigation of 'The Lallantop', this claim turned out to be misleading. Watch the video by the Editor of 'The Lallantop' Saurabh Dwivedi to know the true facts behind the viral misleading claim related to donations during the COVID-19 pandemic.

title: ত্রাণ তহবিলে কে কত টাকা দান করলেন? Bollywood-Tollywood Stars, Sports Persons, Business Man Donation
description:
ত্রাণ তহবিলে কে কত টাকা দান করলেন? Bollywood-Tollywood Stars, Sports Persons, Business Man Donation

✔Official News : http://www.bayofbooks.com/2020/03/blog-post_30.html?m=1


1. Anita Dongre's generous contribution of Rs 1.5 crore
2. Sabyasachi Mukherjee on Saturday also pledged to donate Rs 10 million (Rs 1 crore), Rs 5 million (Rs 50 lakh)
3. Milkha Singh on Friday said his family will donate Rs 2 lakh
4. Sachin Tendulkar on Friday donated Rs 50 lakh
5. Gautam Gambhir on Monday pledged Rs 50 lakh, Lok Sabha MP Gautam Gambhir said that he has released Rs 1 crore out of his MP Local Area Development Scheme
6. Bajrang Punia has also donated his six months salary
7. Anupama Venugopal Nadella, wife of Microsoft CEO Satya Nadella, has donated Rs 2 crore to the Telangana Chief Minister Welfare Fund
8. Tata Sons and Tata Trusts have pledged to contribute Rs 1,500 crore
9. Sourav Ganguly gives away Rs 50 lakh worth of rice
10. Kapil Sharma, who is giving Rs 50 lakh to the Prime Minister’s Relief Fund
11. Punjabi singer Guru Randhawa too contributed to the relief fund. He will be donating Rs 20 lakhs to the fund.
12. Varun Dhawan also pledged to contribute Rs 30 lakh
13. Baahubali star Prabhas also donated Rs 4 crore to the relief funds against the COVID-19
14. TV host and actor Maniesh Paul said he will donate Rs 20 lakh
